und pi-item-spacing\">Chapter Guide</caption>\n\t\n\t<tbody>\n\t<tr>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\" data-source=\"previous\">← <a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_114\" title=\"Chapter 114\">Chapter 114</a></td>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\" data-source=\"next\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_116\" title=\"Chapter 116\">Chapter 116</a> →</td>\n\t\n\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n</section>\n<nav class=\"pi-navigation pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background pi-secondary-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Chapter_115_Images\" title=\"Category:Chapter 115 Images\">Chapter 115 Images</a></nav>\n</aside>\n\n<p></p><p><b>To Be a Hashira</b><span style=\"font-weight: normal\"> (<span class=\"t_nihongo_kanji\" lang=\"ja\"><ruby lang=\"ja\"><rb style=\"text-justify:inter-word\">柱</rb><rp> (</rp><rt>はしら</rt><rp>) </rp></ruby>に</span><span class=\"t_nihongo_comma\" style=\"display:none\">,</span> <i><span class=\"t_nihongo_romaji\">Hashira ni</span></i><span class=\"t_nihongo_help\"><sup><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:Installing_Japanese_character_sets\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Help:Installing Japanese character sets\"><span class=\"t_nihongo_icon\" style=\"color:#198975;font:bold 80% sans-serif;text-decoration:none;padding:0 .1em;\">?</span></a></sup></span>)</span> is the one hundred and fifteenth chapter of <a href=\"/wiki/Koyoharu_Got%C5%8Dge\" title=\"Koyoharu Gotōge\">Koyoharu Gotōge's</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Kimetsu_no_Yaiba_(Manga)\" title=\"Kimetsu no Yaiba (Manga)\">Kimetsu no Yaiba</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Characters_in_Order_of_Appearance\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Characters in Order of Appearance</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Events</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Navigation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Navigation</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Summary\">Summary</span></h2>\n<figure class=\"thumb tleft show-info-icon\" style=\"width: 202px\"> \t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/a/a6/Shizu_attacks_her_children_as_a_Demon_CH115.png/revision/latest?cb=20200524152602\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/Shizu_attacks_her_children_as_a_Demon_CH115.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"121\" class=\"thumbimage\"></a> \t \t<figcaption class=\"thumbcaption\"> \t\t \t\t\t<a href=\"/wiki/File:Shizu_attacks_her_children_as_a_Demon_CH115.png\" class=\"info-icon\"><svg><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-info-small\"></use></svg></a> \t\t \t\t \t\t \t\t\t<p class=\"caption\">Genya and Sanemi's mother attacks her family after turning into a Demon.</p> \t\t \t</figcaption> </figure>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Genya_Shinazugawa\" title=\"Genya Shinazugawa\">Genya Shinazugawa</a> thinks back to his past, where his small and weak <a href=\"/wiki/Shizu_Shinazugawa\" title=\"Shizu Shinazugawa\">mother</a> would often be abused by his father alongside himself and his siblings. One night, Genya notices that she was late coming back even after their older brother, <a href=\"/wiki/Sanemi_Shinazugawa\" title=\"Sanemi Shinazugawa\">Sanemi Shinazugawa</a>, went to look for her. He calms his siblings and tells them to sleep, but they suddenly hear a knock on the door. Genya tries to tell them not to open it in case it was a stranger, but they ignore his word and are immediately slashed upon reaching it. Genya is also cut across the cheek, and he stares in horror at a figure grasping onto the ceiling with the darkness preventing him from identifying it. Suddenly, Sanemi appears and tackles it out the window while yelling at Genya to run.\n</p>\n<figure class=\"thumb tleft show-info-icon\" style=\"width: 202px\"> \t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/c/c9/Sanemi_child.png/revision/latest?cb=20190620192733\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/Sanemi_child.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"209\" class=\"thumbimage lazyload\"></a> \t<noscript><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/c/c9/Sanemi_child.png/revision/latest?cb=20190620192733\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/c/c9/Sanemi_child.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/200?cb=20190620192733\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"209\" class=\"thumbimage\" data-image-name=\"Sanemi child.png\" data-image-key=\"Sanemi_child.png\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/c/c9/Sanemi_child.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/200?cb=20190620192733\" /></a></noscript> \t<figcaption class=\"thumbcaption\"> \t\t \t\t\t<a href=\"/wiki/File:Sanemi_child.png\" class=\"info-icon\"><svg><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-info-small\"></use></svg></a> \t\t \t\t \t\t \t\t\t<p class=\"caption\">Sanemi after killing his Demon-turned mother.</p> \t\t \t</figcaption> </figure>\n<p>Terrified, Genya checks the status of his siblings and tries to cover their wounds, despite their bodies already being cold. When he runs off to find a doctor, he approaches an injured Sanemi standing over the corpse of their demonfied mother. Dismayed at the sight, Genya runs over to cradle his mother's body in his arms and cries, calling Sanemi a murderer.\n</p><p>Genya, after remembering this past, internally apologizes to his older brother for his shock that overwhelmed him to the point of labeling Sanemi as their mother's killer, even despite the struggles that he must've had to protect him by killing her. He recalls an earlier, happier moment with him where they both agreed to defend their mother and siblings as brothers after the death of their abusive father.\n</p><p>As <a href=\"/wiki/Hantengu#Sekido\" title=\"Hantengu\">Sekido</a> aims for Genya's neck, the <a href=\"/wiki/Demon_Slayer_Corps\" title=\"Demon Slayer Corps\">Demon Slayer</a> thinks of all his regrets and flaws. A memory of Sanemi as a <a href=\"/wiki/Hashira\" title=\"Hashira\">Hashira</a> declaring that he had no brother saddens Genya, and he thinks about how he wasn't able to reach Hashira status to earn the right of apologizing to him.\n</p>\n<figure class=\"thumb tright show-info-icon\" style=\"width: 202px\"> \t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/5/5b/Genya_shields_Tanjiro_from_Aizetsu%27s_Blood_Demon_Art_CH115.png/revision/latest?cb=20200410053445\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/Genya_shields_Tanjiro_from_Aizetsu's_Blood_Demon_Art_CH115.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"197\" class=\"thumbimage lazyload\"></a> \t<noscript><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/5/5b/Genya_shields_Tanjiro_from_Aizetsu%27s_Blood_Demon_Art_CH115.png/revision/latest?cb=20200410053445\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/5/5b/Genya_shields_Tanjiro_from_Aizetsu%27s_Blood_Demon_Art_CH115.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/200?cb=20200410053445\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"197\" class=\"thumbimage\" data-image-name=\"Genya shields Tanjiro from Aizetsu&#39;s Blood Demon Art CH115.png\" data-image-key=\"Genya_shields_Tanjiro_from_Aizetsu&#39;s_Blood_Demon_Art_CH115.png\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kimetsu-no-yaiba/images/5/5b/Genya_shields_Tanjiro_from_Aizetsu%27s_Blood_Demon_Art_CH115.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/200?cb=20200410053445\" /></a></noscript> \t<figcaption class=\"thumbcaption\"> \t\t \t\t\t<a href=\"/wiki/File:Genya_shields_Tanjiro_from_Aizetsu%27s_Blood_Demon_Art_CH115.png\" class=\"info-icon\"><svg><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-info-small\"></use></svg></a> \t\t \t\t \t\t \t\t\t<p class=\"caption\">Genya shields Tanjiro from Aizetsu's Blood Demon Art.</p> \t\t \t</figcaption> </figure>\n<p>Right as Sekido scrapes Genya's neck with his staff, <a href=\"/wiki/Tanjiro_Kamado\" title=\"Tanjiro Kamado\">Tanjiro Kamado</a> appears above them and saves him by cutting Sekido's neck. He shouts at Genya to not give up, reminding him that he was supposed to be reaching for the goal of Hashira and that he should only think about beheading <a href=\"/wiki/Hantengu\" title=\"Hantengu\">Hantengu</a>. As Tanjiro finishes speaking, he notices <a href=\"/wiki/Hantengu#Aizetsu\" title=\"Hantengu\">Aizetsu</a> approaching him from behind. The <a href=\"/wiki/Demon\" title=\"Demon\">Demon</a> uses its <a href=\"/wiki/Blood_Demon_Art\" title=\"Blood Demon Art\">Blood Demon Art</a> to attack Tanjiro, but the swordsman is shielded by Genya, who gets impaled at multiple spots on his body. Genya tells Tanjiro that he should be the one to behead Hantengu and Tanjiro accepts, dashing over to Hantengu and hitting him with his flaming sword. Upon being struck, Hantengu lets out a piercing scream.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters_in_Order_of_Appearance\">Characters in Order of Appearance</span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Shizu_Shinazugawa\" title=\"Shizu Shinazugawa\">Shizu Shinazugawa</a></li>\n<li>Genya's father</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Genya_Shinazugawa\" title=\"Genya Shinazugawa\">Genya Shinazugawa</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Sanemi_Shinazugawa\" title=\"Sanemi Shinazugawa\">Sanemi Shinazugawa</a> (memory)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Hantengu#Sekido\" title=\"Hantengu\">Sekido</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Tanjiro_Kamado\" title=\"Tanjiro Kamado\">Tanjiro Kamado</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Hantengu#Aizetsu\" title=\"Hantengu\">Aizetsu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Hantengu\" title=\"Hantengu\">Hantengu</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Events\">Events</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Genya reveals his and Sanemi's past.</li>\n<li>Tanjiro regroups with Genya.</li>\n<li>Tanjiro strikes Hantengu with his red sword.</li></ul>\n\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20210109015249\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.287 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.643 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 9287/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 167964/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 77680/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/40\nExpensive parser function count: 1/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 28/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  349.993      1 -total\n 83.28%  291.475      1 Template:Manga_Navigation\n 81.96%  286.845      1 Template:Navibox\n 37.99%  132.968     26 Template:Navibox/info\n 21.42%   74.959     26 Template:Element_List\n 14.94%   52.289      1 Template:Chapter_Infobox\n  6.52%   22.836     26 Template:Force_Font_Color\n  1.70%    5.951      1 Template:Nihongo\n  0.67%    2.356      1 Template:Ruby\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key prod:kimetsunoyaiba:pcache:idhash:1081-0!canonical and timestamp 20210109015249 and revision id 75569\n -->\n</div>"}